item.title: By: Ben
item.dc:creator: Ben
item.description: Haha. My last name is certainly more what I aspire to be than what I'm able to execute in real life at times; but I'll keep striving for it! I've heard of qigong before but don't practice it myself. I do meditation and workout as my own form of qigong. And to your last point, book learning has its limitations of course, but sometimes you just have to make do with the time you have!
item.content:encoded:
Haha. My last name is certainly more what I aspire to be than what I’m able to execute in real life at times; but I’ll keep striving for it!
I’ve heard of qigong before but don’t practice it myself. I do meditation and workout as my own form of qigong.
And to your last point, book learning has its limitations of course, but sometimes you just have to make do with the time you have!
